details:
**Bug #7 Fix (v1.6.3.1):** Manager Panel doesn't update when Quick Tabs are minimized from their window.

**Root Cause:** VisibilityHandler.handleMinimize() and handleRestore() did not emit `state:updated` events on the internal EventBus.

**Fix:** Added `state:updated` event emission in both methods:
```javascript
if (this.stateManager) {
  this.stateManager.eventBus?.emit('state:updated', {
    quickTab: this._createQuickTabData(id, tabWindow, true)
  });
}
```

**Files Changed:**
- `src/features/quick-tabs/handlers/VisibilityHandler.js`

**Test Verification:**
- Added tests in `tests/unit/handlers/VisibilityHandler.test.js`
